title: The Rebirth World of Warcraft Private Server Client 1.12.1
description:
This contains the WoW client v1.12.1 that already has the realmlist modified to work with The Rebirth's server.  Just install and play (assuming you have an account already created).

I take no credit for this. I'm simply sharing what was available before their website went offline.

This also contains a folder with tons of addons.

Enjoy and please help share! :)
